(2,	'Internal Area',	'## Website\r\n\r\n* [Web pages](/db/webpages)\r\n* [Media](/db/media)\r\n\r\n## Help\r\n\r\n* [Markdown (German)](/hilfe/markdown)\r\n\r\n## Machine Room\r\n\r\n(Access normally not necessary)\r\n\r\n* [Redirects](/db/redirects) – if a web address has changed.\r\n* [Maintenance](/db/maintenance) – administration of everything.\r\n* [Log of database changes](/db/logging)\r\n* [Table relations](/db/relations)\r\n* [Logins](/db/logins)\r\n\r\n## [Logout](/logout/)\r\n',	'/db',	'/',	2,	NULL,	'yes',	'internal',	'&edit=admin',	NOW()),
